###############
# All below could be shared across many sbt projects (on developer machine: https://github.com/flipadmin/command-line-tools/blob/develop/templates/.gitignore-template)

###############
### General ###
# all "hidden" files/folders are most of the time NOT intended to be shared with others, if we want to track any of those we should EXPLICITLY mention them
.*
*.env
!contract-local.env
!.env.template
!.github
!.gitignore
!.remarkrc*.yml
!.sqlfluff
!.sqlfluffignore

####################
### Logs & dumps ###
*.hprof
*.log
**/*-log-*.gz

##############################
